        <div id="section1" class="section">
            <h2>Section 1: Introduction to Post-Construction Cleaning</h2>
            <p>Post-construction cleaning is all about deep cleaning a site after construction or renovation.</p>
            <p>It focuses on:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><i class="fas fa-broom"></i> Removing dust and debris from materials like drywall and sawdust.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Addressing hazards such as nails, screws, or chemicals.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-wind"></i> Tackling hard-to-reach spots like vents and light fixtures.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>Goal:</strong> To make the space safe, clean, and ready for people to move in.</p>
