            <h2>Section 2: Safety Precautions</h2>
            <p>Safety comes first in post-construction cleaning.</p>
            <p>Here are key practices to follow:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><i class="fas fa-hard-hat"></i> Wear protective gear like gloves, goggles, and masks to shield from dust and hazards.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-search"></i> Look out for dangers such as sharp objects or unstable surfaces.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> Report problems like exposed wiring or large debris to a supervisor.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-tools"></i> Use tools like brooms and vacuums safely.</li>
            </ul>
