            <p>Good preparation makes cleaning more efficient.</p>
            <p>Follow these steps:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><i class="fas fa-map"></i> Walk through the site to spot areas that need attention.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-list"></i> Make a checklist of tasks like debris removal and dusting.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-box"></i> Gather supplies such as brooms, vacuums, mops, and cleaners.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Keep tools organized in carts or bins for easy access.</li>
            </ul>
