        <!-- Section 9: Lesson 5 -->
        <div id="section9" class="section">
            <h2>Section 5: Cleaning Floors</h2>
            <p>Floors differ and need specific care.</p>
            <p>Here’s what to do:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><i class="fas fa-broom"></i> For hard floors (tile, wood): Sweep or vacuum, then mop with the right cleaner.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-vacuum"></i> For carpets: Vacuum well, then steam clean for deeper dirt.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-brush"></i> For concrete: Use a heavy-duty cleaner and scrub stains.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-trash"></i> Always remove large debris before starting.</li>
            </ul>
            <button onclick="prevSection()">Back</button>
