        <div id="section15" class="section">
            <h2>Section 8: Cleaning Bathrooms and Kitchens</h2>
            <p>These areas require extra sanitation.</p>
            <p>Here’s what to do:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><i class="fas fa-toilet"></i> In bathrooms: Clean and disinfect toilets, sinks, and floors. Use grout cleaner for tiles.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-sink"></i> In kitchens: Wipe counters, clean appliances, and sanitize sinks.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-sticker-mule"></i> Remove stickers or labels from new fixtures with a scraper or cleaner.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-bacteria"></i> Check for mold—use a bleach solution if you spot it.</li>
            </ul>
            <button onclick="prevSection()">Back</button>
