            <p>Outdoor spaces need attention too.</p>
            <p>Follow these steps:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><i class="fas fa-broom"></i> Sweep patios and walkways to clear debris and dust.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-water"></i> Use a power washer for stained concrete or stone surfaces.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Wipe down outdoor lights, railings, and signs.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-trash"></i> Dispose of waste in heavy-duty bags.</li>
            </ul>
