        <div id="section21" class="section">
            <h2>Section 11: Cleaning Light Fixtures and Vents</h2>
            <p>Light fixtures and vents trap dust that impacts air quality.</p>
            <p>Clean them like this:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><i class="fas fa-power-off"></i> Turn off power first for safety.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-broom"></i> Dust with a duster or vacuum attachment.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-sponge"></i> Wipe fixtures with a damp cloth for glass or metal parts.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Avoid harsh chemicals—they can damage finishes or clog vents.</li>
            </ul>
            <button onclick="prevSection()">Back</button>
