        <!-- Section 23: Lesson 12 -->
        <div id="section23" class="section">
            <h2>Section 12: Cleaning Appliances and Built-In Features</h2>
            <p>New appliances and features need special attention.</p>
            <p>Here’s how:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><i class="fas fa-box-open"></i> Remove packaging like protective films or stickers.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-sponge"></i> Wipe surfaces with a cleaner suited to the material (e.g., stainless steel).</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-vacuum"></i> Clean insides of ovens or cabinets to remove dust.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Test them to ensure no debris affects how they work.</li>
            </ul>
            <button onclick="prevSection()">Back</button>
